%% Customer Management — list/search, add, edit, delete, merge
%% Role gating: Staff is view-only. Add/edit/delete/merge are Admin/Owner only.
%% Phone is a HARD-UNIQUE key (source of truth for public-booking match). Email/name are soft duplicate warnings.
flowchart TD
    Start([Open Customers]) --> List[Customer list<br/>search, filter, sort]
    List --> Action{Choose action}

    %% --- View is open to all roles ---
    Action -->|Open| Profile[Customer profile<br/>details, bookings, history]

    %% --- Any write action requires Admin/Owner ---
    Action -->|Add| CanWrite{Role = Admin/Owner?}
    Action -->|Merge| CanWrite
    Profile -->|Edit / Delete| CanWrite
    CanWrite -->|No| Denied[Action not permitted<br/>Staff is view-only] --> List

    %% --- Add ---
    CanWrite -->|Add| AddForm[New customer form<br/>name, contact, notes]
    AddForm --> PhoneCheck{Phone already exists?}
    PhoneCheck -->|Yes| PhoneBlock[Block — phone must be unique;<br/>open the existing record instead] --> Profile
    PhoneCheck -->|No| DupCheck{Soft duplicate?<br/>match email/name}
    DupCheck -->|Match found| DupWarn[Warn + show matches]
    DupWarn --> DupDecide{Proceed anyway?}
    DupDecide -->|No, open existing| Profile
    DupDecide -->|Yes, create| SaveNew[(Create customer)]
    DupCheck -->|No match| SaveNew
    SaveNew --> Profile

    %% --- Edit ---
    CanWrite -->|Edit| Edit[Edit fields]
    Edit --> ValidEdit{Valid?}
    ValidEdit -->|No| Edit
    ValidEdit -->|Yes| SaveEdit[(Save changes)] --> Profile

    %% --- Delete ---
    CanWrite -->|Delete| DelConfirm{Confirm delete?}
    DelConfirm -->|No| Profile
    DelConfirm -->|Yes| HasBookings{Active/future bookings?}
    HasBookings -->|Yes| BlockDel[Block — resolve bookings first] --> Profile
    HasBookings -->|No| SoftDelete[(Soft delete + retain history)]
    SoftDelete --> List

    %% --- Merge ---
    CanWrite -->|Merge| PickRecords[Select 2+ duplicate records]
    PickRecords --> PickPrimary[Choose primary record]
    PickPrimary --> Resolve[Resolve conflicting fields<br/>pick value per field]
    Resolve --> MergePreview[Preview merged result<br/>combined bookings + history]
    MergePreview --> MergeConfirm{Confirm merge?}
    MergeConfirm -->|No| List
    MergeConfirm -->|Yes| DoMerge[(Merge: move history to primary,<br/>archive secondaries)]
    DoMerge --> Profile
